Package io.boodskap.iot.plugin

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DomainSettings
    An injectable interface, plugin can interact with Boodskap system
    ServiceInterface
    An interface that has to be implemented by plugins of type PluginType.SERVICE
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Config
    Boodskap Plugin Configuration JSON Structure
    ConfigParam
    Plugin configuration parameter
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigParamType
    Supported configuration parameter types
    PluginType
    Type of the plugin being implemented, declared in Plugin.type()
    ServiceType
    Different kinds of supported plugin services
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DomainSettingsResource
    Annotation to access DomainSettings at runtime
    LookupResource
    Annotation to access Boodskap system’s Lookup table
    Plugin
    Every plugin must have this annotation declared
    PluginService
    An annotation to declare on plugins of type PluginType.SERVICE
    PropertyResource
    Annotation to access Boodskap system’s Property table
